<div id="tell_me_how">
  <h1>
    Enter the Omnominator:
  </h1>
  <ul>
    <li>You'll pick some restaurants, from our yelp-powered map (or add your faves).
    </li>
    <li>We'll e-mail the other folks, they'll make their choice, and you'll see the tally.
    </li>
    <li>You can then go have <strong>fried alligator toes</strong> with the reassurance that everyone else is as weird as you. Except maybe Sally.
    </li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    Hey, it's time to eat! Om nom nom nom nom nom nom....
  </p>
</div>
<div id="icanhaznoms">
  <div id="tooltip"></div>
  <div id="yelp_message">&nbsp;</div>
  <div id="map_canvas"></div>
  <form action="#" met hod="get" id="location_form">
